      "value": " \n<p class=\"source\"><b>Source</b> <a href=\"http://amzn.to/2eT3m9D\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PPZO94102</a></p> \n<p><b>Price</b> 35 sp; <b>Weight</b> 15 lb.</p> \n<p>This array of thick, heavily lined pads, including a quilted helmet, rigid shin guards, and a wraparound rib guard, protects you during hand-to-hand training. Sparring gear cannot be worn with <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Armor-Bonus\">armor</a>, but grants <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/universal-monster-rules#TOC-Damage-Reduction-Ex-or-Su-\">DR</a> 2/- against <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Nonlethal-Damage\">nonlethal damage</a>. Fighting schools often customize their sparring gear to feature prestigious colors or symbols.</p> \n",
